 </div> 
</div> 
<p><strong>Frozen Lightning Spear</strong> is an <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Incantations" href="/Incantations" target="">Incantation</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>. <strong>Frozen Lightning Spear spell</strong> conjures a spear from above that moves forward dealing damage and leaving a trail of lightning. Updated to&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patch Notes" href="/Patch+Notes">Patch 1.07</a>.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>Incantation that channels the power of the Dragonkin Soldiers.<br><br>Creates a spear of ice lightning and stabs it into the ground from<br>above. On impact, the spear will burst into trails of lightning advancing forwards.<br><br>The Dragonkin were born in the Eternal City, where they knew<br>no true sky, nor true lightning. Instead, ice lightning was their<br>weapon.</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to find Frozen Lightning Spear</h3> 
<p>Where to find <strong>Frozen Lightning Spear</strong>:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li> <p>Dropped by <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Dragonkin Soldier of Nokstella" href="/Dragonkin+Soldier+of+Nokstella" target="">Dragonkin Soldier of Nokstella</a>. See it on the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=1550&amp;lat=-124.515625&amp;lng=63.418097&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapB" href="/Interactive+Map?id=1550&amp;lat=-124.515625&amp;lng=63.418097&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapB">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a>.</p> </li> 
 <li><a class="wiki_link" title="Video Location" href="https://youtu.be/06r47EyKN08?t=1265">Video Location</a></li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring&nbsp;Frozen Lightning Spear Guide</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Stamina Cost: 45</li> 
 <li>Deals&nbsp;lightning damage</li> 
 <li>One of the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Dragon Cult Incantations" href="/Dragon+Cult+Incantations">Dragon Cult Incantations</a> and is boosted by the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Gravel Stone Seal" href="/Gravel+Stone+Seal">Gravel Stone Seal</a></li> 
 <li>Inflicts Frostbite (120) on opponents.</li> 
 <li>Against large enemies, this attack will hit multiple times, dealing increased damage and frost buildup. A good early game alternative to <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Ancient Dragons' Lightning Strike" href="/Ancient+Dragons'+Lightning+Strike">Ancient Dragons' Lightning Strike</a>.</li> 
 <li><span style="color: #ff6600;"><em>Note:</em></span>&nbsp;As of&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patch Notes" href="/Patch+Notes">Patch 1.07</a>, FP cost reduced from 36 to&nbsp;29, and the frostbite status buildup was&nbsp;increased 90 to 120.</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
