				<li id="16582433" class="cmnt-root" data="4" data-d="1648698053000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><div class="comment-username">Anonymous</div></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t578119/Frozen-Lightning-Spear" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">30 Mar 2022 23:40</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16582433" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">This is one of the flashiest spells in the game, and it actually does more damage than other &quot;posy&quot; lightning spells (the red ones). The thing is that the way it works now, without any added poise whatsoever, makes you very vulnerable while casting. Jumping helps, and you can actually stand still in the air during the cast. And the concept is that the lightning spear you throw to the ground generates a radius of lightning charge (in a cone in front of you) that will hit EVERYTHING within it at the moment of impact. That means that it&apos;s more useful against large bodies enemies, like dragons, since it will actually hit all of the lightning sparks at the same enemy, doing insane damage (and likely procing frostbite). It can be very strong as AoE against mobs too, but it takes some set up (either them being anaware beforehand or doing some poise-breaking stuff like Elden Stars). By the way, Elden Stars followed by this makes you the flashiest caster of all time haha</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16582433" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16582433" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">1</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>6</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>2</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16582433"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16582433" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16582433"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
